repo_description: A simple app to view and filter movies by genres

schemas.name: schema.graphql
schemas.content:
enum Classification {
  UNCLASSIFIED
  GENERAL
  PARENTAL_GUIDANCE
  PARENTAL_GUIDANCE_13
  RESTRICTED
}

enum Genre {
  ACTION
  ADVENTURE
  ANIMATION
  BIOGRAPHY
  COMEDY
  CRIME
  DRAMA
  FAMILY
  FANTASY
  HISTORY
  MUSIC
  MUSICAL
  MYSTERY
  ROMANCE
  SCIFI
  THRILLER
  WAR
  WESTERN
}

type Movie {
  rating: Float
  genres: [Genre]
  classification: Classification
  languages: [String]
  title: String
}

type Query {
  viewer: User
}

type User {
  movieList(genre: String): [Movie]
  allGenres: [String]
}
